{"about_the_game":"<br>You've found yourself in an alternate cyberpunk reality, where every decision is made by the <strong>roll of a di\u0441e</strong>. To get your free will back, you need to find the Perfect Di\u0441e.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Forget everything you've learned from other card games - it won't help you here. The logic of Perfect Dice will definitely twist your brain. Whether you give up or not is entirely up to you, but the reward at the end is worth the journey!</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398430/extras/Manipulations_4.gif?t=1720830526\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Endless possibilities for deck building. You'll need to carefully consider each new card or dice you add to your deck. You can either ruin a great build or, conversely, create an almost ultimate setup that effortlessly defeats enemies left and right.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398430/extras/2024-03-2511.19.04-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1720830526\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A subtle narrative woven into the game invites you to reflect on randomness and its impact on our lives. Do we always need to seek someone to blame, or can we sometimes accept events just as they happen?</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398430/extras/2024-05-0412.19.16-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1720830526\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Top 10","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2398430/c36042a954e8355d361796852aa656252c01076b.jpg"},{"name":"Total Loser","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2398430/e3b7260ee9cc2ff927dfa03bd95e495e0a84e3fb.jpg"},{"name":"Absolute Power","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/